@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@adminToken = dev-admin-token-change-me

### Liveness
GET {{baseUrl}}/health

### Readiness
GET {{baseUrl}}/health/ready

### Service information
GET {{baseUrl}}/api

### Public events
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events

### Public event by slug
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/local-mock-activity-demo

### Public event board
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/local-mock-activity-demo/board

### Public event teams
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/local-mock-activity-demo/teams

### Public event contributions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/events/local-mock-activity-demo/contributions

### Public read-only TempleOSRS refresh request
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/events/local-mock-activity-demo/templeosrs/refresh

### Admin/testing status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Import CSV event signups
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/events/local-mock-activity-demo/signups/import-csv
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "csvText": "Timestamp,Email Address,RuneScape Name,Availability,Daily Hours,Preferred Content,Notes,Team Preference\n2026-07-02T17:30:00Z,player@example.invalid,Sebbe,Evenings,3,Raids,Ready,Blue"
}

### List event signups
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/events/local-mock-activity-demo/signups
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### List event participants
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/events/local-mock-activity-demo/participants
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Create event team
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/events/local-mock-activity-demo/teams
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Blue"
}

### Assign participant team
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/events/local-mock-activity-demo/participants/1/assign-team
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "teamId": 1
}

### Seed local mock activity demo data
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/dev/seed-mock-activity-demo
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Link TempleOSRS competition for an event
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/events/local-mock-activity-demo/external-competitions/templeosrs
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "externalId": "12345",
  "name": "Local Temple Read Cache",
  "metricType": "xp",
  "metricKey": "overall"
}

### List linked external competitions
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/events/local-mock-activity-demo/external-competitions
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Mock activity endpoint
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/activity
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "playerName": "Sebbe",
  "activityType": "item_drop",
  "source": "Theatre of Blood",
  "itemId": 22486,
  "itemName": "Scythe of vitur",
  "quantity": 1,
  "occurredAt": "2026-07-02T18:30:00Z",
  "dedupeKey": "local-demo-scythe-1"
}
